        Description: This is a Quickie HTML viewer and converter, a very
        useful tool for viewing web documents off-line, with hypertext
        linking and colours.  You can also use this program to simply
        convert HTML documents to standard text files.  Uses extended
        memory (XMS) for loading large files.  This program can also be
        used for viewing standard text files.  Copy text to the Windows
        clipboard.  Now comes with the RUNBROWS.EXE program for linking
        to your main web browser (in Windows 95).


                           THIS PROGRAM IS FREEWARE.



           Usage: vh [/b] [filename or search pattern]

            For example:

              vh        (to be prompted for a filename to view)   

              vh filename.htm     (to view file)

              vh /?               (for help)

              vh /b filename.htm  (to convert to .txt)

              vh /b *.htm   (to convert all .htm files to .txt)



